32
00:02:24,878 --> 00:02:27,929
Sometimes It Is Better To Let Your Enemies
Destroy Themselves

33
00:02:27,930 --> 00:02:33,319
Leave your enemy an escape route. A retreat
is the ultimate demoralizing defeat. Let them

34
00:02:33,318 --> 00:02:37,128
be the agents of their own destruction. The
result will be the same.

35
00:02:37,128 --> 00:02:41,158
The risk of crushing an enemy is you embitter
them so much so that they spend years and

36
00:02:41,158 --> 00:03:33,870
years plotting revenge. Do not let your guard
down, but simply crush them again.

